_sText:
Three scientists captured and taken hostage on an island where an unexpected civilian escaped to report captivity to America. 

Now America sends there most efficient bravest soldiers to defeat these terrorists and bring justice back to the island.

Type: Breach map/Hostage rescue

Additional Intel Reports: CTs spawn at the shores of the beach and the Ts spawn in the town. CTs must breach walls and eliminate all threat to reach the target area and rescue the three hostages.
